Created: Hakk1tus 30th of September 2009
E-mail: hakkitus@hotmail.com

Here is beta version of my third map. I worked with this map about 4 weeks now. Map is a bit small but the gameplay will be very fast and full of action. This beta version supports only 50 players but i will fix it up to 64 in final release. While i made this map i have couple usefull ideas to my next map. Hope you enjoy this beta. Have fun!

Please let me know if any kind of bug have been found on it. I will try to release final version of this very soon.

Known bugs: plants looks weird but im working on it. Couple lights are missing.
